    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six. This powerplant maintains peak volumetric efficiency via its individual throttle bodies and a precision-calibrated dual-VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the rear subframe has been structurally reinforced, and rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. The chassis remains composed on Bilstein PSS10 coilover suspension, providing adjustable damping without compromising torsional rigidity. Finished in immaculate Titanium Silver with zero clear-coat failure or oxidation, this example represents a turnkey investment for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
